The package boost-safe-numerics is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS safe_numerics)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::safe_numerics)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_safe_numerics REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::safe_numerics)
